{"tid":2454812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴耀廷已轉往石壁監獄單人倉 友人：他精神不錯","createTime":"2021-03-20T13:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T15:54:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bb654c118ab5e50ec5d909bd904f53550218577d","tid":2454812,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:41:25.000Z","msg":"港大法律學系前副教授戴耀廷因涉及佔中案，被判串謀犯公眾妨擾罪、煽惑他人犯公眾妨擾罪罪成，並在本月初提出上訴，上訴庭裁定撤銷戴的保釋申請。戴的友人向《蘋果》透露，戴已調往石壁監獄服刑，精神不錯，獲「分配工作到釘裝部，可是仍獨住單人倉」。<br />\n<br />\n戴的友人向《蘋果》透露，戴已由荔枝角收押所，調往屬高度設防的石壁監獄服刑，獲「分配工作到釘裝部，可是仍獨住單人倉」，據稱戴的精神「仍然不錯」。<br />\n<br />\n該友人續指，因應疫情關係，親友探訪改為每月兩次，因此除了「戴教授家人探訪外，其他朋友只好寫信給予關懷」，並透過關注囚權的組織「石牆花」把信件轉寄給戴耀廷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/6EL2SEGH5VBUDAWMN6TS4LTQRM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2F6EL2SEGH5VBUDAWMN6TS4LTQRM%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=d90b851a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2F6EL2SEGH5VBUDAWMN6TS4LTQRM%2F&h=cd0f3594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/6EL2SEGH5VBUDAWMN6TS4LTQRM/</a>"},{"pid":"a43ffc819543138b17defc9b98d39b4be87799cc","tid":2454812,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a57b07b88e91254ba3cb7aa7c60e7e7ce2aaff0","tid":2454812,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476a390ec9267124872ba86d216a149348133da7","tid":2454812,"uid":126919,"like":0,"